Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.69,0:00:33.96,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}頑な心のままで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.96,0:00:37.35,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}石ころはどこまで行ける
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:40.71,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}砂のように脆く崩れる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.71,0:00:44.03,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}一文字も読めない未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.03,0:00:46.29,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}don't believe in action
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:50.51,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}ただ前に進むだけじゃ見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:52.86,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}show me your emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:01:00.24,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,666)}言葉の出来ないものを下さい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.50,0:01:03.81,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}一粒の冷たい石に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:07.15,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}秘められた熱もあるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.15,0:01:10.51,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}どうせなら 勝ちに行きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.51,0:01:13.89,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}何もかも見えない未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.89,0:01:16.10,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}you are my illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:20.43,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}空っぽのままの心でもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.43,0:01:22.72,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,666)}show me your addiction
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:26.51,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}閉ざされた夢を探して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.51,0:01:30.30,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}勢い任せで掴んだ手が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:33.56,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}きっと君を変えてくsignal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.56,0:01:36.33,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}会いたくて 飛んだって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:40.19,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,266)}堕ちてゆくけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:43.51,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}もう一度 空を目指して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.51,0:01:46.83,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}放り投げる想いすべて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:49.67,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}泣いだって 分け合って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:52.69,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}君が笑うまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.69,0:01:57.93,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,866)}stone cold
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.91,0:00:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.69,0:00:33.96,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}以一颗顽固的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.96,0:00:37.35,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}石块可以去往任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:40.71,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}如同砂土般轻易崩坏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.71,0:00:44.03,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}无法预知一字的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.03,0:00:46.29,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}don't believe in action
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:50.51,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}如若只是一味向前则会迷失所有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:52.86,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}show me your emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:01:00.24,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,666)}请赐予我无法用语言形容的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.50,0:01:03.81,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}一颗冰冷的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:07.15,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}恐怕也隐藏著炙热的温度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.15,0:01:10.51,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}既然已经决定 那就想要取得胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.51,0:01:13.89,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}空无一物的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.89,0:01:16.10,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}you are my illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:20.43,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}就算只有一颗空洞的心也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.43,0:01:22.72,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,666)}show me your addiction
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:26.51,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}追寻紧闭的梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.51,0:01:30.30,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}把一切交给气势 握紧的双手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:33.56,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}绝对能够改变你的人生signal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.56,0:01:36.33,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}如此思念你 哪怕就算飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:40.19,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,266)}也终会坠落消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:43.51,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}再一次冲上天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.51,0:01:46.83,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}抱紧所有抛下的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:49.67,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}就算哭泣 也一起承担
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:52.69,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}直到你微笑的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.69,0:01:57.93,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,866)}stone cold

