Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.25,0:00:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 周六啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微再睡一会…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.91,0:00:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园祭的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.23,0:00:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好 迟到了

Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:03.97,OT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,500)}学院祭的鬼

Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.77,0:00:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…痛!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园祭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成为新理事长以来的首次重要活动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩下一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何也要撑过去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.04,0:02:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得心跳不已骚动不已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 萌啊萌啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个汉字错了 鬼瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是火焰的燃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军屋的「MOERO OORE」真是效果出众啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.18,0:02:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让大小姐如此干劲十足
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干劲十足…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.94,0:03:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个气氛的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好近 太近了 镜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还想顺势就去握住人家的手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在搞什么呢 太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然突然就跑进来拍照 真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.29,0:03:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我拜托她们的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我拜托她们「留下学院祭记录的」 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 再稍微往左边一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.03,0:03:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 OK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么新理事长的琉璃酱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.39,0:03:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请对明天的学园祭发表一下看法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.71,0:03:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是理事长蓝羽琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.73,0:03:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上任以来的首次学园祭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我衷心希望能够与大家一起尽兴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功办好这个活动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样～可不行～蛋蛋啊鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行喔啊鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我平时跟你说过多少次了 别在普通人的面前说话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急情况啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近有恶石啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学园里?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我腻了 好想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 要是这样都拿不到学分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的成绩就危险了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把我跟你混为一谈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不一样呢 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那个不是丹童子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少善解人意一点 学园祭的时候就别来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说真希望他退学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 我是镜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那边情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才真是失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:05:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让鬼瓦不再淘气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经好好教育过它了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 目标是个什么样的家伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我都能打倒的弱小家伙啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的位置在…这里!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就是你们的披露舞台了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事 等下再去修好就行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 个子高很方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长得高可不是什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早还撞到门楣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还发生了这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还真要命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不痛了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:05:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来准备的很顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃酱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你借我投影机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来宝物的影像上映会就万无一失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.71,0:06:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要让明天的学园祭成功喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一踢那边的足球 它就变成石头了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成石头…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是莫名其妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是恶石没错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.14,0:06:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是说了嘛啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 丹童子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:06:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微陪我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是知道学园暴露在恶石的危险之下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大小姐一定会终止学园祭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果鬼瓦的情报正确的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就靠我一个人应该也能打倒恶石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再怎么弱小 但恶石也是恶石啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.59,0:07:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个想法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 绝对不要告诉大小姐恶石的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你要继续回去社团活动吗啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实感应到的反应很微弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也有进化的可能性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么只要我使用sacred的力量 就能确实打倒它了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试著去拜托琉璃吗啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:08:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说「我要打倒恶石 所以让我变身吧啊鬼」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来学园祭要终止了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 真好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要让明天的学园祭成功喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演一出戏吧啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要欺骗她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.84,0:08:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是演戏而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 要死死盯著她的眼睛说出炙热的台词啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那如同煆烧中瓦片一般的 热烈闪烁的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点燃了我的斗志啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊 琉璃酱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明是理事长 却来帮我做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得做这种事还挺开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事长室？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 是镜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡视结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我是有马
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…有马同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是有马同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是气球破掉的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我有话想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能来屋顶一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口骚动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸…胸口？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.72,0:09:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没事 我马上去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么待会见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学院内发现了恶石
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入警戒状态
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动动态检测跟热源探测
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各感测器 没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始传送资料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步热源解析与动态检测的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶石不会有热源反应啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 立即把契约装甲派来学院
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在学生面前出动装备…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有专门为了这种时候存在的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Operation Mirrorforce吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Operation Mirrorforce？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 这个任务不能告诉大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.29,0:10:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说找我有事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.69,0:10:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有马同学         那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是            我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想更加熟练的使用sacred的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想为了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不对 是为了大家而使用这份力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 这个想法太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在能让我变身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.71,0:11:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之能当练习啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许还能帮忙解决大家的困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那热烈闪烁的眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的不算
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习的话 用备用品就足够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 这些备用品得多少钱啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得这个好像是1亿4千万
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1亿？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.54,0:11:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有4千万呢啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之记忆聚集我身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:12:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之「意志」赐予你身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.02,0:12:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.95,0:12:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子…同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 难不成你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 部长 事情是这样的…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice cosplay啊 丹童子同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:13:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我正为社团的宣传伤脑筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 你这身打扮的话 宣传效果一定很惊人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说是吧 琉璃酱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.69,0:13:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 也许真是如此喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣传吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:15.41,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你著迷的石头 记录 石头的24小时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Operation Mirrorforce 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 要加油啰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来心情很不错啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.82,0:13:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有马同学终于有干劲了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕她没想到背后居然是我在牵线搭桥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 速度怎么这么快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子 变身了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接到大小姐的联络 说是为了训练才变身的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 脸颊好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 给我好好道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 增加了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:48.31,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:49.76,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他原来是这种角色吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先追这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标变成两个了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该是恶石分裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:14:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棘手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜同学 你在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真亏你们能做出这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在正在执行任务 所以无暇顾及你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能请你们尽快回活动室去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被这样露骨拒绝的话 反而让人更想去看个究竟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.06,0:15:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不快点就来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…丹童子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然搞这么夸张的cosplay
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.74,0:15:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来 我扔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 差不多就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.99,0:16:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事情了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作纪念牌的时候发生了事故
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能想点办法下来？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.44,0:16:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快救救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们下来的时候为什么不帮他一把
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.04,0:16:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得想个办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是又不能在众目睽睽之下使用Sacred Seven的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.18,0:16:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 解决掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一只
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子那家伙在搞什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撑住 救援马上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:16:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能放松力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:16:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经到极限了 不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位同学 别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对英雄而言没有不可能的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 丹童子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:17:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的太感谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得比起我们 还是丹童子更善良啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把恶石扔过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于收拾掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有什么困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们英雄都会干净俐落地解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 收工
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:20:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 原来是拍电影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:01.28,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是拍电影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Operation Mirrorforce
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mission complete
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然不向我报告 到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我解释一下 镜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为应该优先排除恶石
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万幸没出什么大事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你没想过会波及到学生们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.35,0:20:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是为了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别说多余的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.57,0:20:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了能让你所期待的学园祭成功举办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子 你也一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.19,0:20:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我发誓再也不会瞒著我跟恶石战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:20:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:20:59.07,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.47,0:20:59.07,SP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命　　　　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.14,0:21:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我很感谢你们能保护了学院祭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很感谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 不介意的话 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 正好肚子饿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.22,0:21:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以全吃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要留下我那份啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学院祭那天 天公作美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,众多来宾大驾光临
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.71,0:21:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们矿石部也盛况空前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在文化部的展览中获得了第二名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我推荐的「记录 石头的24小时」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.92,0:21:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出人意料的没什么人气 真是遗憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.21,0:21:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子们明明都很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:49.51,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜同学 再靠左边点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.12,0:21:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说 学院祭无事终了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:51.57,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}表彰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:51.57,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}COSPLAY特别奖 丹童子有马殿下 镜诚殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:51.57,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}你在第一届蓝羽学园祭COSPLAY部门中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:51.57,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}就如正文所述 获得了优异的成绩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:51.57,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}在此对你们进行表彰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:51.57,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}蓝羽学园 学园祭施行委员会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实丹童子同学和镜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也因为前几天的活跃而受到了好评
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:21:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了COSPLAY特别奖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.19,0:22:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要结束了呢 真是意犹未尽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.52,0:22:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近这饮料卖得很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.25,0:22:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的真清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我家是开药店的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.97,0:22:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个真的那么好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.07,0:22:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个饮料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.47,0:22:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎么了 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.59,0:22:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事都没有！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.61,0:22:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是您的脸色…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.55,0:22:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通红啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.05,0:22:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连有马同学也…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.47,0:22:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丢脸

